{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2aa8a605f1","title":"康生对宁夏军区的指示","origin":"宁夏回族自治区无产阶级文化大革命（文件汇编），宁夏无产阶级革命派总指挥部、宁夏自治区革命工人代表大会政宣部合编，一九六八年元月二十七日","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9c7a610318","index":0,"year":1967,"month":12,"day":null,"articleId":"2aa8a605f1"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"57eea82497","name":"康生","type":"人物"},{"id":"e208109710","name":"宁夏文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"8bb7755376","name":"康生"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9c47e9912a","type":"title","text":"康生对宁夏军区的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2aa8a605f1"},{"id":"1efe181999","type":"authors","text":"康生","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2aa8a605f1"},{"id":"fe7b174a02","type":"appellation","text":"（宁夏军区副司令员张怀礼同志传达）","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2aa8a605f1"},{"id":"4e20de0731","type":"paragraph","text":"一、筹备处派代表去北京谈判，不是搞重庆谈判，是受教育。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2aa8a605f1"},{"id":"e4ba7cdf67","type":"paragraph","text":"二、加强宣传，报纸、电台、宣传车，对中央首长关于宁夏问题的谈话、兰州军区公告，要反复宣传，把有线广播搞起来（特别是电台有线广播）。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2aa8a605f1"},{"id":"4e37e46e0e","type":"paragraph","text":"三、不要抓头头，抓来要放。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2aa8a605f1"},{"id":"8fbd4a5984","type":"paragraph","text":"四、适当的分发武器，要武装造反派，如果他们对银川进行反扑，坚决自卫。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2aa8a605f1"},{"id":"b16467310d","type":"paragraph","text":"五、筹备处破坏铁路，康老很生气，把朱声达叫去训一顿。这是反革命事件。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2aa8a605f1"},{"id":"8f37abb0b3","type":"paragraph","text":"六、第三势力对自己参加谈判的代表数量少，他们很有意见，中央说可以考虑。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2aa8a605f1"},{"id":"092b677f08","type":"paragraph","text":"七、继续用飞机散发传单。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2aa8a605f1"}],"page":{"id":"81003cd7f9","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2aa8a605f1","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}